      <acqinfo>
        <head>Acquisition Information
</head>
        <p>Materials were donated by John L. Heatwole in December, 1987. The gift agreement defines Carrier Library as the permanent repository for Heatwole's artistic papers, and states that he will make continuing
donations of non-current materials over time.
</p>
